### Auto-Expand Panel Requirements (User Request)
- **Default state**: Recent entries section starts at smallest size (0px - fully closed)
- **Auto-expand**: When entries are added, panel automatically expands upward to show them (up to max height)
- **Manual override**: If user manually drags to resize, size locks at that value until user changes it
- **Persistence**: Settings saved to IndexedDB / .brain export (already handled by useTimeTrackingPanelStore)

